Here is the HTML code for the responsive navbar with dropdown:
```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Responsive Navbar</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		}

		.navbar {
			background-color: #333;
			padding: 10px;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			align-items: center;
			position: relative;
		}

		.navbar ul {
			list-style: none;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: row;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.navbar li {
			margin-right: 20px;
		}

		.navbar a {
			color: #fff;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		.navbar a:hover {
			color: #ccc;
		}

		.dropdown {
			position: absolute;
			background-color: #333;
			padding: 10px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			display: none;
			z-index: 1000;
		}

		.navbar li:hover .dropdown {
			display: block;
		}

		.dropdown ul {
			list-style: none;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.dropdown li {
			margin-bottom: 10px;
		}

		.dropdown a {
			color: #fff;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		.dropdown a:hover {
			color: #ccc;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<nav class="navbar">
		<ul>
			<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">About</a></li>
			<li class="dropdown">
				<a href="#">Dropdown <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></a>
				<ul class="dropdown">
					<li><a href="#">Dropdown Item 1</a></li>
					<li><a href="#">Dropdown Item 2</a></li>
					<li><a href="#">Dropdown Item 3</a></li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
		</ul>
	</nav>

	<script>
		const dropdowns = document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown');

		dropdowns.forEach((dropdown) => {
			dropdown.addEventListener('mouseover', () => {
				dropdown.classList.add('show');
			});

			dropdown.addEventListener('mouseout', () => {
				dropdown.classList.remove('show');
			});
		});
	</script>
</body>
</html>
```
Note: You'll need to add a font-awesome CDN link or import the font-awesome library for the caret-down icon.
